<section
  class="py-10 md:pt-[2.5rem] md:pb-[4.5rem] shadow-2xl relative bg-blueTropezon"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div
      class="flex justify-between items-center pb-10 lg:pb-0"
      data-x-data
      data-x-ref="popularToursTitle"
      data-x-intersect="anime({ targets: $refs.popularToursTitle, translateY: [100, 0], opacity: [0 , 1], easing: 'linear', duration: 500 })"
    >
      <div class="">
        <h2 class="titular-principal text-white mt-2 md:mb-8 uppercase">
          Wide range of <br />
          entertainment and <br class="hidden md:block" />
          culture offerings
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-20">
      <!--1-->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-y-10 lg:gap-y-0 lg:flex-row justify-between"
      >
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center items-center">
          <div
            class="border lg:border-l-0 lg:border-t-0 lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r-0 border-orangeTropezon px-10 lg:px-0 py-10 flex flex-col gap-y-5 relative"
          >
            <div
              class="border border-l-0 border-orangeTropezon absolute top-0 -left-96 lg:w-[53rem] xl:w-[59rem] 2xl:w-[62rem] h-[16rem] hidden lg:block"
            ></div>

            <p class="text-white parrafo tracking-widest lg:pr-1 xl:pr-8">
              “The socio-cultural profile of San Antonio de Areco is incredible.
              The diversity and culture present there are very interesting. It
              is the birthplace of some of the best artisans and goldsmiths in
              the country. Many visual artists, musicians and writers from
              Argentina have settled there.”
            </p>
            <div class="md:flex flex-col items-start gap-x-4 hidden">
              <span
                class="text-orangeTropezon parrafo flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 tracking-widest"
                ><hr class="border-t border-orangeTropezon w-[2.5rem]" />
                Juan Cruz Talia, owner of El Tropezón </span
              ><span class="text-orangeTropezon parrafo tracking-widest"
                >de Areco.</span
              >
            </div>

            <div class="md:hidden flex flex-col items-start gap-x-4">
              <span
                class="text-orangeTropezon parrafo flex items-center justify-center gap-x-2 tracking-widest"
                ><hr class="border-t border-orangeTropezon w-[2.5rem]" />
                Juan Cruz Talia, owner of El Tropezón de Areco
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-2/3 mx-auto lg:w-1/3 flex justify-center lg:justify-end items-center relative"
        >
          <div class="swiper-containers-cultura-areco overflow-hidden">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <!-- Imagen repetida 5 veces -->
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-cultura-0.jpg"
                  alt="Imagen 1"
                  class="w-full"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-cultura-1.png"
                  alt="Imagen 2"
                  class="w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-cultura-2.png"
                  alt="Imagen 3"
                  class="w-full"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-cultura-3.png"
                  alt="Imagen 3"
                  class="w-full"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Agrega los botones de navegación -->
          <div class="swiper-button-next absolute"></div>
          <div class="swiper-button-prev absolute"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!--2-->
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse justify-between gap-y-10">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center items-center">
          <div class="lg:pr-10 flex flex-col gap-y-5 lg:text-right">
            <h1 class="titular-principal text-orangeTropezon uppercase">
              The Festival of Tradition
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white font-tradeGothicLt tracking-widest parrafo">
              Every year in November, the Day of Tradition is celebrated with
              live music, dances, traditional food, a parade at Plaza Ruiz de
              Arellano and various activities at Parque Criollo. The bravest
              gauchos compete in the rodeo events known as "jineteadas," which
              are as dangerous as they are spectacular!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-2/3 mx-auto lg:w-1/3 flex justify-center lg:justify-end items-center relative"
        >
          <div class="swiper-containers-tradicion-areco overflow-hidden">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <!-- Imagen repetida 5 veces -->
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-tradicion-1.jpg"
                  alt="Imagen 1"
                  class="w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-tradicion-2.png"
                  alt="Imagen 2"
                  class="w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide flex justify-end">
                <img
                  src="../../../assets/img/galeria-areco-tradicion-3.png"
                  alt="Imagen 3"
                  class="w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Agrega los botones de navegación -->
          <div class="swiper-button-next absolute"></div>
          <div class="swiper-button-prev absolute"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
